languages.text: "Обладание и движение, неудержимость и упоение. Мы поняли. Мы будем думать об этом".
"Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."
languages.original_text: "Обладание и движение, неудержимость и упоение. Мы поняли. Мы будем думать об этом".

traits.locale_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

languages.text: « Possession et mouvement, irrépressibilité et volupté... Nous comprenons, désormais. Nous allons y réfléchir. »
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

traits.locale_text: « Possession et mouvement, irrépressibilité et volupté... Nous comprenons, désormais. Nous allons y réfléchir. »

languages.text: “占有与运动，不可抑制之物与愉悦。我们现在理解了。我们会思考它的。”
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

traits.locale_text: “占有与运动，不可抑制之物与愉悦。我们现在理解了。我们会思考它的。”

languages.text: "Besitz und Bewegung, Ununterdrückbarkeit und Entrückung. Wir verstehen jetzt. Wir werden darüber nachdenken."
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

traits.locale_text: "Besitz und Bewegung, Ununterdrückbarkeit und Entrückung. Wir verstehen jetzt. Wir werden darüber nachdenken."

languages.text: «La posesión y el movimiento, lo incontenible y la euforia. Ahora lo entendemos. Esto nos dará que pensar».
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

traits.locale_text: «La posesión y el movimiento, lo incontenible y la euforia. Ahora lo entendemos. Esto nos dará que pensar».

languages.text: 「所有と移動、抑えがたいものと歓喜。やっと理解できた。しばらくこのことについて熟考させてもらう」
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."

traits.locale_text: 「所有と移動、抑えがたいものと歓喜。やっと理解できた。しばらくこのことについて熟考させてもらう」

languages.text: "Mülkiyet ve hareket, önlenemezlik ve coşku... Şimdi anlıyoruz. Bunu düşüneceğiz."
languages.original_text: "Possession and movement, irrepressibility and rapture. We understand now. We will think about this."
